<div class="faq_section qure__section color-background"
    style="--section-padding-top: 80px; --section-padding-bottom: 80px; --section-background: #F6F6F7; --section-padding-top-mob: 50px; --section-padding-bottom-mob: 50px;"
    id="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="qure__section-header text-center">
            <h2 class="qure__section-heading">Have questions?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_content">
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="qure_faq-main">
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-1" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-1">
                        How does the Qure Q-Renew LLLT Helmet work?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet uses a combination of low-level laser therapy (LLLT) and red LED
                                light therapy to help energize hair follicles and support healthier-looking, fuller
                                hair. The lasers deliver focused light deeper into the scalp, while LEDs provide broader
                                coverage</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-2" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-2">
                        How often can I use this treatment?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>We recommend using the helmet 3-4 times per week for at least 16 weeks. After that,
                                continue every other day to maintain results.</p>
                            <p>Each treatment lasts 12 minutes and ends automatically.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-3" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-3">
                        How quickly will I see the results?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Visible changes take time. Most users should expect to use the helmet consistently for at
                                least 3-6 months before noticing fuller, healthier-looking hair. Like any long-term
                                treatment, consistency is key!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-4" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-4">
                        Can I use it while it is charging?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-4" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>No. The helmet will not operate while charging. Always unplug before use.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-5" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-5">
                        How long does it take to charge?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-5" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>A full charge takes about 4 hours. The helmet is powered by a rechargeable 3.7V, 5000mAh
                                lithium-ion battery.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-6" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-6">
                        Is Q-Renew LLLT Helmet safe and FDA cleared?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-6" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Yes, the Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is safe and FDA-cleared. </p>
                            <p>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is indicated for the promotion of hair growth in males who have
                                Norwood-Hamilton classifications of IIa-V, and in females with androgenetic alopecia who
                                have Ludwig-Savin Classifications of I-II, and in both, Fitzpatrick Classification of
                                Skin Phototypes I to IV.</p>
                            <p>It features built-in safety sensors that only activate the lights when the device is
                                properly positioned on your head. It will automatically pause if removed. The warmth is
                                mild, with a maximum of 35°C (95°F).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-7" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-7">
                        Who is it not recommended for?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-7" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Do not use this product if you are under 18, pregnant, breastfeeding, photosensitive, on
                                light-sensitizing medications, prone to light-triggered headaches or seizures, or have
                                open wounds or infections on the scalp.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-8" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-8">
                        Does Q-Renew LLLT Helmet come with a warranty?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-8" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Yes, the Q-Renew LLLT Helmet comes with a 2-year warranty.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-md-50 pt-40 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-3">
